headline: 3D Systems Announces Major Milestones in Saudi Arabian Growth Initiative
summary: NAMI, the 3D Systems–Dussur joint venture, reached critical milestones in deploying advanced 3D printing across Saudi Arabia’s energy and defense sectorsSaudi Electric Company, the Middle East’s largest electricity producer, signed an agreement to make a strategic investment in NAMI, acquiring 30% stake in expanded joint ventureLockheed Martin entered into collaboration with NAMI to qualify and manufacture critical military and aerospace components in Saudi Arabia for use in international market

headline: A Look at NioCorp Developments (NasdaqGM:NB) Valuation Following Lockheed Martin Alliance and U.S. Federal Support
summary: NioCorp Developments (NasdaqGM:NB) is making headlines after unveiling a strategic alliance with Lockheed Martin’s Skunk Works division. The $10 million U.S. Department of War award supports this move to boost America’s critical minerals supply chain. See our latest analysis for NioCorp Developments. NioCorp's share price has soared lately, climbing 21.1% in the past month and an extraordinary 443% year-to-date, as investors responded to a flurry of government-backed initiatives and progress...
